author: Graphic Designer 2
title: Indians looking to slow down Trojan offense
text: Indians looking to slow down Trojan offense By KEVIN BRUCHHAUS Daily News Staff Writer ELTON – Elton High School (EHS) head football coach Doyle Carter explained his squad’s big district 4-1A showdown against the East Beauregard (EBHS) Trojans Friday night would more than likely be decided by which team’s offense could keep the ball away from the other. For the fifth time this season, the Indians will face a double-wing offense that makes its living grounding out wins three yards a pop. Problem is, the Trojans have managed to be just a little bit better than everybody else in doing that.  //www.jenningsdailynews.net/?p=34304   15
